SUMMARY:Explore Spiritual Freedom with Eckankar at the 2026 Festival of Light!
DESCRIPTION:Roanoke Spiritual Experiences Group\nLocation:\nBoonsboro Ruritan Club\n1499 Coffee Road\nLynchburg VA 24503\nDescription:\nAre you ready to enhance your spiritual journey or curious about reincarnation? Learn how to find divine love in everyday life and explore the special connection you have with your pet\, because animals are Soul too! Visit us at the ECKANKAR Booth to share stories of love and coincidences\, learn about the spiritual benefits of the ancient teachings of ECKANKAR\, the Path of Spiritual Freedom\, and discuss your favorite animals and their spiritual significance. Take a spin on the ECK Wisdom Wheel to see what divine message comes through for you.\nA flyer for this event is available at:\n[https://eck-va.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/L-Burg-Poster-Spring-Festival-of-Light-021526.pdf](https://eck-va.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/L-Burg-Poster-Spring-Festival-of-Light-021526.pdf)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/roanoke-spiritual-experiences-group/events/313553467/
